  "_comment": "Default Stapel theme (frontend-guardrails §1). SOURCE OF TRUTH — code (tokens.css/tokens.ts/tailwind.css) is generated from this file via `pnpm gen:tokens` and drift-gated by `pnpm gen:tokens:check`. A host copies this to `stapel.theme.json` and edits it; absence of a host file = this default. THREE LEVELS: (L1) `ramps` = custom raw ramps merged over the built-in standard ramps (ramps.standard.json) — hex is born here and NOWHERE else; (L2) `core` = semantic tokens, each EXACTLY a {light,dark} pair of `<ramp>.<step>` refs (unpaired or hex ⇒ build error); (L3) `component` = component tokens, each EXACTLY one core-token ref (emitted as a var() reference, so light/dark ends at L2 and a theme-dependent component token is syntactically impossible). `scales`/`elevation` are the non-colour tokens on the same source.",
